
The page window manager is a tiling window manager that like your mouse.

To use this overlay you have to install layman:

 # emerge layman

add this unofficial overlay :

 # layman -o https://raw.github.com/gschwind/page-overlay/master/repositories.xml -f -a page

and finaly emerge page :

 # emerge page

You can find the page documentation to:

http://www.hzog.net/index.php/Main_Page

